apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1

        containers:
          - name: a

            command: [ sh, -c ]
            args: [ echo, hi, /workspace/out ]

            image: argoproj/argosay:v2

            args: [ echo, hi, /workspace/out ]
```

v3.4.1 / helm chart 0.20.1
